<script type="text/javascript">

    var collectedErrors = [];
    (function() {
        var previousOnError = window.onerror;
        window.onerror = function(message, source, line, column, error) {
            if (collectedErrors) {
                error = error || new Error(message);
                console.info("Collecting unhandled error \"" + error + "\"");
                collectedErrors.push(error);
            }
            if (previousOnError) {
                return previousOnError.apply(window, arguments);
            }
        };
    })();

    window.dctk = window.dctk || {};

    (function( window, logging, undefined ) {
        logging.pageStartTime = new Date().getTime();

            'hotel-search-tray-item-template.hbs', 'hotel-tray-item-template.hbs', 'package-tray-item-template.hbs', 'scratchpad'], function($) {
            Scratchpad.init();
          });
        }
      });
    }
  </script>

  window.alertMenuClickHandlers = {
    flightMIPGT: function(){
        if (window.AlertsMenu) {
            AlertsMenu.sendeVar28('Header.Notif.LX.Flight.GT');
        }
    },

    flightMIPActivity: function(){
        if (window.AlertsMenu) {
            AlertsMenu.sendeVar28('Header.Notif.LX.Flight.Activity');
        }
    },

    spSignIn: function(e, alertItemRef) {
        if (window.AlertsMenu) {
            AlertsMenu.sendeVar28('Header.Notif.SP.SignIn');
        }
    },
    spNudgeEnroll: function(e, alertItemRef) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();

        var $target = $(e.target).closest('.alert-item');

        $target
            .find('.close-button')
            .remove();

        $target
            .find('.alert-message')
            .html('We\'ll send Scratchpad updates to you by email. Watch your inbox!');

        if (Scratchpad.state.loggedInUser) {
            uitk.utils.liveAnnounce('We\'ll send Scratchpad updates to you by email. Watch your inbox!');
        }

        if (window.uitk
        && window.uitk.utils
        && window.uitk.utils.focusElement) {
            uitk.utils.focusElement($target);
        }

        if (window.AlertsMenu) AlertsMenu.sendeVar28('Header.Notif.SP.OptIn');
        if (window.Scratchpad) Scratchpad.enrollInNudge();
    },
    spBasicNews: function(e, alertItemRef) {
        if (window.AlertsMenu) {
            AlertsMenu.sendeVar28('Header.Notif.SP.News');
        }
    },
    spDetailedNews: function(e, alertItemRef) {
        if (window.AlertsMenu) {
            AlertsMenu.sendeVar28('Header.Notif.SP.LiveAlerts');
        }
    }
  };

   /*===========Accessible Strings============*/
  window.accessibleBadgeMessage = "You have 1 notification";
  window.accessibleBadgeMessagePlural = "You have {0} notifications";
  window.accessibleNotifClose = "Close";
</script>

(function() {

    var page = ['device.device.type', 'pageInfo.language', 'activityId', 'activityName', 'currencyCode', 'checkout.cartTotal.amount', 'bookingDateinUTC', 'carVendor', 'carType', 'carPickUpLocationCode', 'carDropOffLocationCode', 'cruiseLine', 'cabinClass', 'cruiseTitle', 'departureMonth', 'carrierCodes', 'lengthOfFlight', 'starRating', 'guestRating', 'hotelBrand', 'hotelName', 'hotelId', 'numberOfRooms', 'roomType', 'roomDescription', 'packageType', 'SiteBrand', 'pointofsales', 'pageType', 'lob.domain', 'siteName', 'siteId', 'adults', 'childrenCount', 'numberOfGuests', 'destination', 'regionId', 'destinationAirportCode', 'origin', 'originAirportCode', 'bookingWindow', 'lengthOfStay', 'checkInDate', 'checkOutDate', 'city', 'state', 'stateProvinceCode', 'country', 'countryCode', 'roomNights', 'isInternationalBooking', 'tripType'];

    var user = ['rewardsStatus.membershipTier', 'loggedUser', 'device.device.type', 'context.user.expUserProfileId', 'pageInfo.language', 'context.marketingAttribution.restrictedLastTouch', 'tuid', 'guid', 'checkout.trl', 'checkout.customerFacingItineraryNumber'];

    var checkOver = function(arr, dl, type) {
        var i, len = arr.length;
        for (i = 0; i < len; i++) {
            if (arr.hasOwnProperty(i) && dl[arr[i]]) {
                dataObj[type][arr[i]] = dl[arr[i]];
            }
        }
    };

    if (window.utag_data) {
        var dl = window.utag_data;
        var dataObj = {
            page: {},
            user: {}
        };
        checkOver(page, dl, 'page');
        checkOver(user, dl, 'user');
        var omitKeys = '',
            custDelimit = '',
            prefix = '',
            config = {
                'userKeys': user,
                'omitKeys': omitKeys ? omitKeys.split(',') : [],
                'customDelimited': custDelimit ? custDelimit.split(',') : undefined,
                'caseSensitive': true,
                'useFullPath': true,
                'useLastValue': false,
                convertAttrNames: [{
                    pattern: /page_attr_page.carDropOffLocationCode|page_attr_page.destinationAirportCode/,
                    replacement: 'page_attr_page.mergedDestinationCode'
                }, {
                    pattern: /page_attr_page.originAirportCode|page_attr_page.carPickUpLocationCode/,
                    replacement: 'page_attr_page.mergedOriginCode'
                }, {
                    // the following two attributes are ingested both as page and user attributes, but for some reason the data layer ingester marks them always as user attributes, renaming the attributes here explicitly solves the issue
                    // the reason for ingesting them as two types is to built up the page attribute population and then deactivating the user attribute
                    pattern: /user_attr_page.device.device.type/,
                    replacement: 'page_attr_page.site.platform'
                }, {
                    pattern: /user_attr_page.pageInfo.language/,
                    replacement: 'page_attr_page.language'
                }]
            };

        if (!prefix.match(/^$|null|undefined|false/)) {
            config.convertAttrNames.push({
                pattern: /((?:page|user)_attr_)/,
                replacement: '$1' + prefix
            });
        }
        config.omitKeys.push(/gtm\./);
        Krux('ingestDataLayer', dataObj, config);
    }

})();
